## Import

Multi cluster app can be imported using the multi cluster app ID in the format `<multi_cluster_app_name>`

```sh
 $ pulumi import rancher2:index/multiClusterApp:MultiClusterApp foo &lt;MULTI_CLUSTER_APP_ID&gt;
```
